This test verifies that styled.global rules flow through the aggregator
exactly: each [@@@css ...] becomes a line in styles.css, with `var()`
substitutions intact, and the dynamic `:root` block does NOT appear.

  $ refmt --parse re --print ml input.re > output.ml
  $ standalone --impl output.ml -o output.ml
  $ styled-ppx.generate output.ml > styles.css
  $ cat styles.css
  /* This file is generated by styled-ppx, do not edit manually */
  body{color:var(--primary-1n85yzx);margin:0;}
  html{box-sizing:border-box;}
